<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>Car parking is available in front of the main hospital building, and also in the large car park near the outpatients department. For patients who have appointments in the McNeill Suite, there is a car park to serve this area. To park here, turn left shortly after entering the hospital drive. </p>
